00790 void print_paranoid(paranoid *paranoid,FILE *file)
00791 {
00792         unsigned int name;
00793         fprintf(file,"->KEY:%08lX\t BLOCK:%d\t TABU LIST ELEMENT:%d\n",paranoid->key,paranoid->block,paranoid->tabu);
00794         name=paranoid->list->name;

00800                 paranoid->list=paranoid->list->next;
00801         }
00802 }
